	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=196365><span id=Sage>NYKnight</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>22 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.95]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>To answer the below question, this book is not found, but rather combined from the Torn Burnt Book and the Torn Frost Covered Book. These two books drop off the following:<br><br>Frost Covered Book drops off Gorenaire in the Dreadlands, Lady Vox in Permafrost and Faydedar in Timorous Deep.<br><br>Burnt Book drops off Severilous in Emerald Jungle, Lord Nagafen in Nagafen's Lair, Talendor in Skyfire, and Melafen in Western Wastes.<br><br>If you are too low a level to go on a dragon raid? No problem, ask around, chances are someone else has the Book of Scale and it is still not no drop so you might get lucky as the dragons are dropped on a regular basis, or heck, go to the bazaar in case someone is trying to make a quick buck off it.<br><br>Sir Enhmet Silvershield<br>65 Lord Protector of Marr <br>Twists of Fate<br>Povar Server</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
